{"title":"Dana White demands Peloton bikes removed from UFC gym over past conflict with comedian Theo Von Ffff you, Peloton","uid":"a8ce066572c37b1787920d047942e0b9","slug":"dane-white-hate-peloton","date":"2023-11-24T05:36:58.000Z","updated":"2026-02-22T13:03:20.473Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/dane-white-hate-peloton.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ReBc_kGV6IQ/maxresdefault.jpg","content":"<h2 id=\"Dana-White-demands-Peloton-bikes-removed-from-UFC-gym-over-past-conflict-with-comedian-Theo-Von-Ffff-you-Peloton\"><a href=\"#Dana-White-demands-Peloton-bikes-removed-from-UFC-gym-over-past-conflict-with-comedian-Theo-Von-Ffff-you-Peloton\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Dana White demands Peloton bikes removed from UFC gym over past conflict with comedian Theo Von  Ffff you, Peloton\"></a>Dana White demands Peloton bikes removed from UFC gym over past conflict with comedian Theo Von  Ffff you, Peloton</h2><h1 id=\"Dana-White’s-Pedal-Powered-Protest-at-UFC\"><a href=\"#Dana-White’s-Pedal-Powered-Protest-at-UFC\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Dana White’s Pedal-Powered Protest at UFC\"></a><strong>Dana White’s Pedal-Powered Protest at UFC</strong></h1><h2 id=\"No-More-Peloton-Rides-at-UFC-Performance-Institute\"><a href=\"#No-More-Peloton-Rides-at-UFC-Performance-Institute\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"No More Peloton Rides at UFC Performance Institute\"></a><strong>No More Peloton Rides at UFC Performance Institute</strong></h2><p>UFC’s head honcho, Dana White, has just laid down the law: It’s goodbye to Peloton bikes at the UFC Performance Institute. This drastic move comes after a comedic twist involving Theo Von and a controversial podcast episode.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/hIOnUkAl4goVy0kbpN7zJX0aQbA=/1400x1050/filters:format(jpeg)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25089425/1744596275.jpg\" alt=\"Dana White\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"The-Peloton-Problem\"><a href=\"#The-Peloton-Problem\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"The Peloton Problem\"></a><strong>The Peloton Problem</strong></h3><p>Here’s the scoop: Theo Von, a comedian and podcast host, was sponsored by Peloton. But trouble brewed when Peloton got twitchy over an episode featuring Robert Kennedy Jr. Dana White’s reaction? A no-holds-barred verbal takedown of Peloton and their CEO, Barry McCarthy.</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>“So Peloton, what do they sell? <strong>Freakin’ stationary bikes?</strong>“ - Dana White</p></blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"The-Great-Peloton-Purge\"><a href=\"#The-Great-Peloton-Purge\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"The Great Peloton Purge\"></a><strong>The Great Peloton Purge</strong></h3><p>Dana didn’t just stop at fiery words. He called in Craig Borsari, UFC’s EVP of Ops, and made it clear:</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>“We’re getting rid of the Pelotons. Pelotons are out of the gym. That’s what you do. You stop using their products.”</p></blockquote>\n<p>This isn’t Dana’s first rodeo with corporate clashes. He recalled a time a major sponsor tried to censor his political support and got a similar treatment.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O5oC9iYn6bI\">Dont miss the video i clipped of the greatest part!! </a></p>\n<h3 id=\"The-Aftermath\"><a href=\"#The-Aftermath\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"The Aftermath\"></a><strong>The Aftermath</strong></h3><p>Fast forward to the present: UFC’s gym is now a Peloton-free zone. And Barry McCarthy? Well, he’s probably rethinking that statement about everyone wanting to partner with Peloton, especially after Dana’s fiery retort:</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>“You sell stationary bikes, you clown. That guy is the typical pompous, arrogant jerk that I cannot stomach.” - Dana White</p></blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"https://mediadc.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/02dd4b1/2147483647/strip/true/crop/7573x4260+0+0/resize/1200x675!/quality/90/?url=http://mediadc-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com/6d/da/e0ec97604288b30ebfacece9e688/ap23187829458425.jpg\" alt=\"Dana White\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"Peloton’s-Rocky-Road\"><a href=\"#Peloton’s-Rocky-Road\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Peloton’s Rocky Road\"></a><strong>Peloton’s Rocky Road</strong></h3><p>Peloton’s journey isn’t all smooth riding. They’ve hit a financial snag, with a hefty net loss and a plummeting stock price. Despite recent partnerships with the NBA and WNBA, Dana White’s UFC has made it clear: They’re not fans.</p>\n","feature":true,"text":"Dana White demands Peloton bikes removed from UFC gym over past conflict with co...","permalink":"/post/dane-white-hate-peloton","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.9k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"news","slug":"news","count":2,"path":"api/categories/news.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"bored","slug":"bored","count":1,"path":"api/tags/bored.json"},{"name":"work","slug":"work","count":1,"path":"api/tags/work.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-ite